content:
what would be nice is to settle relatively soonish on a JSON format for this message, something as simple as 
```json
{
  "message": {
    "validator_index": 7654,
    "from_bls_pubkey": "0x...6f8e2ae4008e867",
    "to_execution_address": "0x....ab973"
  },
  "signature": "0x912ab4f..."
}
```
Would probably do, but having a standard that these tooling generates would be nice so that clients just implement importing a file and not the signing itself
